GROUP BY will group all the rows that have the same query name 
Quality Calc = SUM(q.rating/q.position) / COUNT(*) . In this we are finding the aggregate of rating/position and then taking the average
Poor Query Percentage = 

ROUND(
    (
      SUM(CASE WHEN rating < 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END)
      / COUNT(*)
    ) * 100,
    2
)


SUM(CASE WHEN rating < 3 THEN 1 ELSE 0 END) -> Counts rows which have rating < 3
Then divide by total rows and then take percentage

